From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2020 11:13:49 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] mac80211: populate debugfs only after cfg80211 init
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.6.8
Git-commit: 6cb5f3ea4654faf8c28b901266e960b1a4787b26

[ Upstream commit 6cb5f3ea4654faf8c28b901266e960b1a4787b26 ]

When fixing the initialization race, we neglected to account for
the fact that debugfs is initialized in wiphy_register(), and
some debugfs things went missing (or rather were rerooted to the
global debugfs root).

Fix this by adding debugfs entries only after wiphy_register().
This requires some changes in the rate control code since it
currently adds debugfs at alloc time, which can no longer be
done after the reordering.

